author_ssm: Megan O'Shea and Molly A. Cross
unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Africa Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Africa Serials contains over 50 titles published in Africa, the United States, and Europe on political, cultural, and social issues in sub-Saharan Africa between 1951 and 2009.  The bulk of the collection consists of serials published between the 1970s and the 1980s on South Africa and anti-apartheid movements in Africa, the United States, and the United Kingdom.
